description:
This is a 21 minute workout called 'Whole Body Circuit' from the channel Peter Donohoe.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Endorphin Wave and The Meditative Grind vibe.
The The Endorphin Wave vibe means Elevated energy, feel-good movement, steady build. This is especially good for When you want a challenging but steady burn. The The Meditative Grind vibe means Zone in, lock down, let repetition take over. This is especially good for Those who love a slow burn and rhythmic intensity..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Fire up your lower body and core with Peter in this whole-body circuit overlooking downtown Florence....
